      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i run a small local hardware store in a pretty rural part of ohio. i've been seeing a lot of news about these proposed hikes to the minimum wage lately and i'm kinda worried. can you explain how increasing the minimum wage usually impacts small businesses in areas where the cost of living isn't that high?",
