    "summary": "A small business owner in rural Ohio expresses concern about minimum wage hikes, questioning whether economic research accounts for the disproportionate burden on family-owned shops compared to large corporations. The assistant initially provides a balanced view on the economic trade-offs but eventually validates the user's specific political/economic grievance in the final turn.",
